                    "The world was at war, during this time"
                ]
            },
            {
                "id" : 1,
                "image" : "C3-S2",
                "dialogue" :
                [
                    "To prevent blimps from attacking the cities,",
                    "The army filled the skies with air mines",
                    "Air mines were balls covered in spikes"
                ]
            },
            {
                "id" : 3,
                "image" : "C3-S3",
                "dialogue" :
                [
                    "They would drift through the sky",
                    "dutifully warding off attacking blimps"
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
    {
